headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Take Two Interactive (TTWO) After 40% One Year Rally?
summary: If you are wondering whether Take-Two Interactive Software is richly priced or still offers value, this article walks through what the current share price might be implying. The stock recently closed at US$250.71, with returns of 1.9% over the past 30 days and 40.4% over the last year, while the year to date move sits at a 0.4% decline.
